Package: ThermoPheno
Type: Package
Title: Thermal-Time-Based Crop Phenology Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mohammad Reza Eini", "User", email = "mreiniut@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    ThermoPheno is a thermal-time-based phenology model for simulating crop 
    growing seasons under historical and climate change conditions. It includes 
    a Shiny application and a set of functions for estimating thermal time, 
    crop maturity, and growing season dynamics.
